18 horses will be part of the race, with two being reserves. The Reserves are to be scratched by 8:15, Friday 30th of June. Should a horse in the top 18 not be able to race, it will simply be replaced by the reserve horses.

Bet with Hollywoodbets

Hollywoodbets Durban July this year is a renewal event, as it's the first Hollywood Durban July to happen unrestricted in 3 years. The event will be at Hollywoodbets Greyville Racecourse in Durban and is expected to have 50, 000 participants.

Grade 1, the race of races with the grand prize of R5 million, is the event everyone will ultimately be anticipating. The Grade 1 special is the 7th race of the day and starts at 1600 p.m. The winner of the race will perform a victory canter, which is when a horse moves faster than a trot but slower than a gallop, which of course represents overcoming other racing opponents, something like a victory lap.

The Hollywoodbets Durban July winner will enter the Gold Horseshoe Winner’s Box in front of the grandstand, and after that, there’ll be a presentation of silver salvers and sashes.

3.1

Hollywoodbets Durban's July 15% Deposit Bonus

This year's Durban July plans to be out of this world, and with that comes a 15% deposit bonus on all deposits up to R20 000, with the maximum bonus being R3 000. The following conditions apply to this appealing bonus:

The Durban July 15% bonus promotion will run on all deposits made between June 23, 2023, 00:00 and July 2, 2023, 23:59 which is 10 days;

The Bonus is only valid for Hollywoodbets account holders;

The 15% bonus only applies to deposits up to R20,000, so once the maximum bonus of R3 000 is credited to the player's account, no further deposits above R20 000 from the player will qualify for any bonus;

Bonuses will be credited to the account only once Hollywoodbets has received the deposit and confirmation of the deposit from the relevant payment provider;

The HollywoodBets bonus is a great incentive, providing players with more entertainment and winning possibilities.

3.2

Hollywoodbets Punters' Challenge

The Hollywoodbets Punters Challenge, which only applies to Durban's July 1 Hollywoodbets Greyville race day, is available to anyone who is an account holder at Hollywoodbets and wants to stand a chance to win a share of R20 million. The winner will receive R200 000, while the runners-up and 3rd place will receive R80 000 and R40 000, respectively. Players can enter the Punters Challenge at any point, up to 5 minutes before the first race at the respective venue.

3.3

Full Steam Ahead

The Theme of this year's Hollywood Durban July event is “out of this world,” inviting attendees to be taken to the stars and beyond. The celestial theme intends to make this year's Durban July Spectacular, and with the event having been restricted for the last 3 years due to COVID, this year's event is set to be truly memorable. The 2023 Hollywood Bets Durban July tickets are now available, with tickets for general admission available for R230 from Ticketpro or any SPAR Payzone Kiosk in the nation. There will also be tickets available that will grant you access to secure parking on the golf course for an extra R170. The Grade 1 event is the 7th race on Saturday, starting at 16:00 p.m. with a grand prize total of R5 000 000. Spectators can expect to win big and have a great and entertaining time.

Bet with Hollywoodbets

3.4

Hollywoodbets Durban July Bonanza

A chance to win a Golf 8 GTI, cash prizes, and VIP HDJ experiences with the Hollywoodbets Durban July Bonanza is available for everyone this year. Anyone can easily enter the bonanza by:

Simply playing R15 or more on horse racing;

Opt in on the promotion page just once for all bets to be entered;

Players must further take note of the following applicable conditions:

The competition is open from May 5 at 00:00 to July 12, 2023;

The cutoff time for submissions is 23:59 on July 9, 2023;

The final draw date for the competition is July 12, 2023;

Betting ticket numbers can only be used within the promotion period;

Customers must place a horse racing bet for R15 or more by using their online betting account or play at a Hollywoodbets branch for R15 or more and opt-in on the promotions page just once for all bets to be entered. For branch bets, customers will need to dial *120*46559*2*ticketnumber#;

Each ticket number can only be entered once;

The prizes include 1 VW Golf GTI, a share of R250 000 cash, and 5 VIP experiences to the Hollywoodbets Durban July;
